dtc (0.36.1-1) experimental; urgency=low

  * New upstream release with these changes:
    [ Thomas Goirand ]
    - Bugfix: Fixes cron job PHP Notice.
    - Do not create symlinks to domains folders anymore.
    - Bugfix: Restores correct unix rights in /var/lib/dtc/etc/template.
    - Bugfix: Stops configure mysqmail with the (not in use) syslog_file option
    - Generate a random password if install/upgrade is made in non-interactive
    mode.
    - Added the dtcgrp group in the sbox creation.
    - Added few alt text in img tags (for blind people use).
    - Bugfix: Missing conf_force_use_https global in gen_pro_vhosts.php.
    - Now uses a bigint for the ftp_accounting transfer field.
    - Bugfix: Fixes Vhost generation issue for parked domains (see
    http://bts.gplhost.com/mantis/view.php?id=131).
    - Bugfix: Added updateUsingCron("gen_qmail='yes'"); in the email panel.
    - Bugfix: Fixed missing $panel_type="cronjob"; in backupcron.php.
    - Bugfix: Do not allow users to write an email instead of a mailbox when
    creating a new email address.
    - Fixed link with empty subject of support tickets.
    - Added a --insecure to the curl call in user_migrate.sh to allow self
    signed certs.
    - Added some HTML5 placeholder in the email.php and templates.php.
    - Added the current running status of VPSes in renewals.php.
    - Clean up the mailing list, so that it is using the themes as well.
    - Allows translated MLMMJ list text to be copied in a list to configure
    it with the correct language.
    - Adds more theming and graphics to both the email and lists screens.
    - Adds HTTP statistics break down per subdomain in domain stats.
    - Sets force_use_https to on by default.
    - Bugfix: do not generate a IN A record for a subdomain if it starts
    with _ (but continue to allow it for TXT records).
    - Bugfix: Calls triggerDomainListUpdate() when a customer adds a domain
    from My Account.
    - Added a mail queue purge script.
    - Sets bounce_msg of pop_access as utf8 charset, so that vacation msgs
    can be in any language.
    - Added dumps of MySQL procedures (using --routines option to mysqldump)
    when migrating.
    - Also uses --routines in the gen_backup_script.php
    - Adds --skip-extended-insert when dumping dbs.
    - Added new Italian translation thanks to Lorenzo Bencini.
    - Added a small script to massively convert sites to sbox.

    [ Shuki Vaknin ]
    - Added hebrew translations.

    [ Jeremy Cayrasso ]
    - fix file deletion and net_restor during backup.
    - Fix ipv6 firewall.

    [ Martin Thomas Schrott ]
    - changed some fuzzy translations for german and added some missing
    strings.
    - Solved a little bug that did create serveraliases for the wildcarddomains
    of parkeddomains not just for the domain but also for its subdomains.
    - German translations update.
    - Added user configurable email based spam and content filter configuration
    for postfix/amavis-new/spamassassin.
    - Added various options to the admin, client and email panel.

    [ Gregory Fardel ]
    - Many corrections to the French translation of DTC.
    - delete_user.php : Also remove the dns zone file of the deleted domain
    name.

    [ Javier Marcon ]
    - Fix send mail on cron fail option to be showed on configuration.
    - Added Cuenta Digital payment gateway.
    - Added to dtc-client the posibility to add hosting products, new domains
    to an existing user, email accounts, add database users and add databases.
    - Add image url for cheque and wiretransfer payment gateways.
    - Add image url for paypal payment gateway.
    - allow product hide if is enabled the option to force of product_id in
    the request of new_account.
