    - Add Western Union and abitab payment gateways.
    - Add confirm to client delete.
    - Add subdomains folder to ftp creation.
    - Avoid deleting the default subdomain.
    - Expired and not expired totals in renewals.php.
    - Add the posibility to send registration mail to the customer.
    - Options to hide some fields for my_account.
    - Archive or delete new admins.

    [ Jesse Norell ]
    - Add auto-response support for Auto-Submitted: headers per rfc3834.
    - Try to prevent auto-reply spam in mailbot auto-replies.
    - Include message's Subject in sieve vacation reply.
    - Escape vacation text and spam mailbox name in sieve script.
    - Sets ownership of /var/lib/roundcube/temp
    - Honor php resource settings for dtc admin site.
    - Add wget user-agent to dtc-user-cron.
    - Bugfix: Create sieve dir before try to use it.
    - Sieve creates missing spambox
    - dovecot: Subscribe to mailboxes that are automatically created.
    - Add smtpprox-loopprevent support.
    - Add migrate-mailman-list-to-dtc.sh contrib script.
    - Add reject_non_fqdn_hostname in the postfix directives.

