    - Add Windows Compatibility option tu subdomains.
    - Localize radio values on edits.
    - Update spanish translation.
    - Add domain alias support to dovecot login.
    - Add custom part to DNS Zones.
    - Respect Default Zone TTL on all generated files.
    - Parametrize reverse_zones path to do the same as in forward zones
    - Add list_reverse_dns to list_domains.php using named.conf.slave.reverse
    already generated.
    - Fix reverse zone name generation for "One zone file per pool with name"
    - Split Admin Editor in Admin Editor itself and Add/Delete Services Screen.
    - Delete function for custom products.
