    - Add webmail hostname redirect.
    - Add option to transfer only forward, reverse or both zones to
    slavezone_update (contrib script folder).
    - Add an optional client admin panel subdomain direction.
    - Add SPF record support on DNS with a standard default.
    - Create radio button to enable/disable/auto-enable-disable admin, add
